{"tid":1463803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「有滲透之時，和平或成最大力量」","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:15.000Z","uid":72597,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e970d670e4abe6436e102d11316c99ca197dcfc6","tid":1463803,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"亂鬥亂<br />\n對家一定狠過我地<br />\n因為佢地目標就係要我地亂<br />\n<br />\n我地鬥唔過，反會被人從中作梗，一舖清袋<br />\n各位手足為保唔好一子錯 滿盤皆輸<br />\n為左更<span style=\"color: orange;\">任重道遠</span>嘅考慮<br />\n忍住，保持克制<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我地玩緊聲譽籌碼，咁就跟翻聲譽條路黎玩</span><br />\n唔該<br />\n愛你三千<br />\n<br />\n曾經我都好嬲左膠<br />\n但<span style=\"color: orange;\">做水 唔係得流動性<br />\n仲可以由硬挖嘅冰，變成溫和嘅霧</span>"},{"pid":"21880a9e1d667dff5bcd116034b1e1741710544d","tid":1463803,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68a56bce88ca2aa911c87552a869d5f333ca303a","tid":1463803,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42f67dfbae401cd03817218f8d0f4c5acfe0d993","tid":1463803,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"a1fdc7bb383e4b3cf940a73ae2d4e59c817d600b","tid":1463803,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:50:56.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"84d90792fd35a7b74a22d662d994c28178e4438d","tid":1463803,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfd96c9494194f647a9a70e2fca920d16ad91b2f","tid":1463803,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2d524abdbaa6459f16aa511faf98ee8030ca510","tid":1463803,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da7869f018b108f44d87743ff821cb856e2774fe","tid":1463803,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cbb56080b0cc87268c67e0f0be4fb536b39da07","tid":1463803,"uid":298186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n無保充"}]}